---
title: Double Chicken & Roast Veggie Dhal with Garlic Tortilla Chips & Yoghurt
description: No wonder dhal is the darling of Indian home cooking – it's nutritious, versatile, easy to make and brimming with flavour.
Here, we're adding tender pieces of chicken, sweet roasted parsnip and carrot, and crunchy garlic flatbread chips.
